{"tid":363830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台北世大運選手村 賽後變青年住宅只租不售","createTime":"2017-08-18T02:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T02:32:36.000Z","uid":55981,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"823eb8e6b888ce425d11b391be6c8a8f7a1dcd74","tid":363830,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:03:25.000Z","msg":"台北世大運的選手村由34樓樓宇，是全新建築，大部份是三人一間apartment的設計，世大運結束後，大會會將選手村用作社區住宅，預計有3,000戶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170818/large/1503018862_619e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170818%2Flarge%2F1503018862_619e.jpg&h=37ce1245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170818/largel/1503018863_c128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170818%2Flargel%2F1503018863_c128.jpg&h=527ba477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170818/large/1503018865_f0de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170818%2Flarge%2F1503018865_f0de.jpg&h=5edc0426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170815/420_4ac14e0637f8a4d9fb2e9ca5d802216b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170815%2F420_4ac14e0637f8a4d9fb2e9ca5d802216b.jpg&h=29966e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170815/420_f27a773b8fb52b84314cb925c42f5316.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170815%2F420_f27a773b8fb52b84314cb925c42f5316.jpg&h=63307490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170815/420_9c2d75ab8332e0f206bee74d952431ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170815%2F420_9c2d75ab8332e0f206bee74d952431ec.jpg&h=1c3262aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n針對議員關心世大運選手村的社會住宅問題，朱市長表示，已與內政部溝通，選手村3,408戶希望未來全數轉為社會住宅，至少是只租不售；且指不管將來是哪個單位管理，要設立住宅法人或是行政法人，新北市民都會受益。"},{"pid":"892c86c7c7686ef2e2afb392ab2ed1adcb3b3d82","tid":363830,"uid":55981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qIqKrIqBOBc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqIqKrIqBOBc&d=HqpLf98MxpKEHguAnJT33NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f781ec67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qIqKrIqBOBc</a><br />\n<br />\n中和青年社會擁有3個全國第一，基地面積最大（約1公頃）、戶數最多（816戶），也是第一個結合「公共托育中心」及「市民活動中心」等社會福利空間的社會住宅。本次816戶中，其中3房50戶、2房76戶及套房690戶，臨近公園、學校、生活便利，在大台北生活圈打拼通勤的青年朋友一個很好的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n民眾最關心的租金，為考量市民經濟可負擔能力，弱勢戶套房11.5坪最低7100台幣起，2房22.7坪最低1萬3200台幣起， 3房34坪最低1萬8600台幣起，最高不超過2萬台幣，一般戶也都低於市場行情8折以下，套房8800台幣起、2房1萬6200台幣，租金均已包含家具、家電及管理費，不用再擔心額外加價。"},{"pid":"cb5b51ca3cc1e7076c14b5ba086b97455e4908ae","tid":363830,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:14:34.000Z","msg":"新北青年大舉進駐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e6e560beeb93a2fff256e73e7941a1b4cfd6dd","tid":363830,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"Hall G"},{"pid":"09439781b75702a850d5d0dd5db68dc3a631ddf5","tid":363830,"uid":68040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:29:59.000Z","msg":"全國最大炮房中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望到都覺得淫亂"},{"pid":"b34d816fe33092638c0d3594f2cb92eb06df75c0","tid":363830,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"410呎，月租$1839"}]}